ype\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/fairmount-pet-shoppe\",\"name\":\"Fairmount Pet Shoppe\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/fairmount-pet-shoppe\",\"description\":\"Pet supply shop featuring food, toys & accessories, plus adoption events for dogs, cats &...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Philadelphia\",\"addressRegion\":\"PA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":8,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/ham-bone-queen-village\",\"name\":\"ham + bone Queen Village\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/ham-bone-queen-village\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in Philadelphia rave about ham + bone Queen Village, giving it a solid 4.8-star rating based on 32 reviews. What makes this facility special is its clean and well-maintained, convenient...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Philadelphia\",\"addressRegion\":\"PA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":9,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/litterpaw-pet-supply-washington-square-west\",\"name\":\"Litterpaw Pet Supply - Washington Square West\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/litterpaw-pet-supply-washington-square-west\",\"description\":\"Quaint pet supply shop featuring food, toys & other items, plus sitting services & food...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Philadelphia\",\"addressRegion\":\"PA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":10,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/salty-paws-rittenhouse-square\",\"name\":\"Salty Paws Rittenhouse Square\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/salty-paws-rittenhouse-square\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in Philadelphia rave about Salty Paws Rittenhouse Square, giving it a solid 4.8-star rating based on 60 reviews. What makes this facility special is its clean and well-maintained,...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Philadelphia\",\"addressRegion\":\"PA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How many dog parks are available in Philadelphia?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Philadelphia has 18 dog parks and dog-friendly establishments, including traditional outdoor dog parks, indoor dog parks, and dog-friendly businesses like restaurants and shops. Each type offers unique benefits for different situations and dog personalities.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are there any indoor dog parks in the USA?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes! The United States is home to hundreds of indoor dog parks, and the industry is growing rapidly. IndoorDogPark.org maintains the most comprehensive directory available, currently tracking over 360 verified facilities across 155 cities nationwide. These climate-controlled spaces solve real problems for dog owners. In cities like Phoenix where summer temperatures can exceed 110°F, or Chicago where winter brings sub-zero temperatures for months, indoor parks become essential. They're also invaluable in rainy regions like Seattle or Portland, where outdoor parks stay muddy for much of the year. Our directory includes detailed profiles for each facility: amenities, pricing structures, operating hours, vaccination requirements, and real visitor experiences. We've aggregated over 106,000 user reviews from Google, Yelp, and other platforms to help you make informed decisions. Popular metro areas with the most options include Los Angeles (23 indoor facilities), Chicago (18 facilities), and New York City (15 facilities). But we've also documented smaller markets like Bend, Oregon, and Asheville, North Carolina, where innovative entrepreneurs are meeting local demand. To explore options near you, visit our main directory page or browse by state. Each listing includes photos, direct contact information, and links to facility websites where you can check current availability and make reservations.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are dog parks in Philadelphia free to use?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Most traditional outdoor dog parks in public spaces are free to use. However, indoor dog parks and specialized facilities typically require membership fees or day passes. Dog-friendly establishments like restaurants may have minimum purchase requirements or special pet menus.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What are the requirements to visit dog parks in Philadelphia?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Most dog parks require that your dog be current on vaccinations (rabies, DHPP), licensed, and well-behaved. Some indoor facilities may require proof of vaccinations, health certificates, or temperament assessments. Always check specific park rules before visiting.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What's the best time to visit dog parks in Philadelphia?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Early mornings (6–9 AM) and early evenings (4–7 PM) are typically the busiest times, offering great socialization opportunities. Midday visits are usually quieter, better for dogs who may be overwhelmed by crowds. Weekends are generally busier than weekdays. Consider your dog's personality and social comfort level when planning visits.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Where to go with a dog when it's raining?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Rainy days don't have to mean canceled playtime. Indoor dog parks are specifically designed for exactly this scenario, offering climate-controlled environments where dogs can exercise and socialize safely. Our directory lists over 360 indoor facilities across the country. Many feature specialized surfaces like K9Grass or rubberized flooring that stay clean and dry regardless of weather. These surfaces are easier on joints than concrete and reduce injury risk compared to muddy outdoor parks. Beyond dedicated indoor parks, consider these alternatives: • Pet stores with play areas: Chains like PetSmart and Petco sometimes host indoor play sessions. • Dog-friendly cafes and restaurants: Many now welcome well-behaved dogs indoors, perfect for socialization in a calmer setting. • Indoor training facilities: Often open their spaces for play sessions between classes. • Doggy daycare centers: Many offer drop-in playtime options for non-members. Pro tip: Indoor facilities get significantly busier during bad weather, so call ahead or book reservations when possible. Many also offer online booking systems for convenience. Bonus: Most indoor parks include dog wash stations, so your pup can get clean before the ride home—no muddy paws in your car. Explore our directory to find indoor options near you, and filter by amenities like \\\"dog wash\\\" or \\\"separate small dog areas\\\" to find exactly what you need.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are there any size restrictions or separate areas for different sized dogs?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Many dog parks in Philadelphia offer separate areas for small dogs (under 25 lbs) and large dogs (over 25 lbs). This helps ensure safe play experiences. However, not all parks have this separation, so it's important to check ahead and supervise your dog's interactions.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What should I bring when visiting a dog park in Philadelphia?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Essential items include: a leash (for entering and exiting), poop bags, fresh water and a bowl, your dog's vaccination records (especially for indoor facilities), and your phone for emergencies. Optional items include toys (check park rules first), treats for training, and a first-aid kit.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are there indoor dog park options available in Philadelphia?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Not yet in our verified directory for Philadelphia. If you know a great indoor option, you can submit it and we’ll review it for inclusion.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What is the most dog friendly city in the USA?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"This question sparks lively debates among dog owners, and the answer depends on what you value most. Based on our analysis of over 360 facilities across 155 cities, here's what the data reveals: California dominates in sheer numbers: Los Angeles, San Diego, and San Francisco collectively host 50+ indoor dog parks. But quantity isn't everything. Cities consistently ranking high for overall dog-friendliness include: • San Francisco: Over 40% of households include dogs (above the 38% national average), extensive off-leash beaches, and one of the highest concentrations of dog parks per capita. • Portland, Oregon: Known for progressive pet policies, abundant green spaces, and a culture where dogs are welcome almost everywhere—including many restaurants and breweries. • Seattle: Over 14 off-leash areas plus multiple indoor facilities, making it ideal for a city that gets 150+ rainy days annually. • Austin, Texas: Boasts some of the largest dog parks in the country, plus a vibrant dog-friendly dining scene. • Denver: High altitude doesn't stop Coloradans—the city maintains excellent park facilities and welcoming policies. However, \\\"friendliness\\\" extends beyond park counts. Factors like pet-friendly rental policies, veterinary care access, breed restrictions, and community culture matter just as much. Our directory lets you explore by city to see specific offerings. Check out our city guides for detailed breakdowns of parks, amenities, and local pet policies. We also maintain guides for major metro areas on our blog, covering everything from best parks to dog-friendly neighborhoods.\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Dog Parks Directory\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Philadelphia\"}]}</script><header class=\"header header-visible  header-light\"><div class=\"header-container\"><div class=\"header-left\"><a class=\"logo\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Indoor Dog Park logo\" width=\"140\" height=\"40\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent;object-fit:contain;height:auto\" src=\"/images/logo/logo.png\"/></a></div><div class=\"header-center\"><nav class=\"header-nav\" aria-label=\"Main navigation\"><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/\">Browse Parks</a><div class=\"header-nav-item\"><button class=\"header-nav-link\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Discover <i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down dropdown-icon \"></i></button><div class=\"header-dropdown \"><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/parks-with-bars\">Parks with Bars</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/training-facilities\">Training Facilities</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/how-it-works\">How It Works</a></div></div><div class=\"header-nav-item\"><button class=\"header-nav-link\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Locations <i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down dropdown-icon \"></i></button><div class=\"header-dropdown \"><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/san-francisco\">San Francisco</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/los-angeles\">Los Angeles</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/san-diego\">San Diego</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/new-york\">New York</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/seattle\">Seattle</a></div></div><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></nav></div><div class=\"header-right\"><a class=\"header-link\" href=\"/contact\">Contact us</a><a class=\"header-link header-link-primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">List your park</a><a class=\"header-link\" href=\"/signup\">Sign up</a><a class=\"header-link\" href=\"/login\">Log in</a><button class=\"menu-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><i class=\"bi bi-list\"></i></button></div></div><div class=\"mobile-menu \" aria-hidden=\"true\"><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/\">Browse Parks</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/parks-with-bars\">Parks with Bars</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/training-facilities\">Training Facilities</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/how-it-works\">How It Works</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/blog\">Blog &amp; Guides</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/contact\">Contact us</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/list-your-park\">List your park</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/signup\">Sign up</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/login\">Log in</a></div></header><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 table-of-contents \"><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-progress-bar\"><div style=\"width:0%\" class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-progress-fill\"></div></div><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-container\"><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-header\"><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-title\">Table of Contents</div><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-subtitle\">Jump to any section</span></div><nav class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-nav\"><ul class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-list\"><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">1</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">City Overview</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">2</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Quick Facts</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">3</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Top Comparisons</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">4</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Park Collections</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">5</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Neighborhoods</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">6</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Park Type Guide</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">7</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Map &amp; Neighborhoods</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">8</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Planning Essentials</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">9</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Expert Advice</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">10</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Full Directory</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">11</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Owner &amp; Franchise</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">12</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">FAQs</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">13</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">More Resources</span></button></li></ul></nav><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-actions\"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn toc-action-top\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-up\"></i>Back to Top</button><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-down\"></i>To Bottom</button></div></div></div><main class=\"city-page-layout\"><div class=\"mobile-toc-button\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"mobile-toc-trigger\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-ul\"></i><span>Contents</span></button></div><section id=\"city-hero\" class=\"city-hero-section \"><div class=\"section-shell city-hero-shell\"><div class=\"city-hero-copy\"><div class=\"hero-breadcrumbs\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><span>Dog Parks Directory</span><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><strong>Philadelphia</strong></div><p class=\"hero-eyebrow\">City spotlight</p><h1>Indoor Dog Park in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania</h1><p class=\"hero-description\">Whether you are hiking the vast trails of Wissahickon Valley or relaxing in Rittenhouse Square, Philadelphia blends history with high-quality pet amenities.</p><div class=\"city-rich-description\"><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">Philadelphia, the City of Brotherly Love, extends that affection to its canine residents through a wealth of urban green spaces and historic charm. Adventurous pups will love <strong>Wissahickon Valley Park</strong>, which boasts over 50 miles of trails, including the scenic Forbidden Drive. In the heart of the city, <strong>Schuylkill River Park</strong> offers a popular enclosed dog run with separate sections for small and large breeds, ensuring a safe environment for all. For a more relaxed afternoon, leashed dogs are welcome in the historic <strong>Rittenhouse Square</strong> or can join you for a stroll through the <strong>9th Street Italian Market</strong>. Philadelphia’s leash laws require a six-foot lead in all public areas unless specified as an off-leash zone, and the city strictly enforces waste removal to keep its parks beautiful.</p><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">The <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://phillypaws.org/\">Philadelphia Animal Welfare Society (PAWS)</a> works tirelessly as the city’s largest rescue partner, focusing on finding forever homes for pets in need. Owners can also look to <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.acctphilly.org/\">ACCT Philly</a> for lost and found resources. Beyond the parks, many local breweries and eateries, such as those in the Fishtown or Old City neighborhoods, offer dog-friendly patios and even special treats for furry visitors. For comprehensive tips on living with pets in an urban environment, visit <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\">Indoordogpark.org</a>. Whether you’re heading to the rooftop at <strong>Cira Green</strong> for a dog-friendly movie night or exploring the meadows of <strong>Pennypack Park</strong>, Philadelphia provides an enriching urban experience for dogs and their owners alike.</p></div><div class=\"hero-cta-row\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta primary\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-check\"></i>Browse directory</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta ghost\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i>Open map</button><a class=\"hero-cta text-link\" href=\"/list-your-park\"><i class=\"bi bi-plus-circle\"></i>Submit a park</a></div><div class=\"hero-footnotes\"><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Data refreshed weekly</span><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Live availability coming soon</span></div></div><div class=\"city-hero-visual\"><div class=\"hero-image-card\"><img alt=\"Philadelphia dog park landscape\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/philadelphia-pa/hero.webp\"/><div class=\"hero-image-gradient\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"city-premium-section\" aria-labelledby=\"city-premium-heading\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"city-premium-header\"><div><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Premium spotlight</span><h2 id=\"city-premium-heading\">Premium parks in <!-- -->Philadelphia</h2><p>Partners highlighted here are currently investing in featured placement across this guide.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-header-actions\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">Feature my park</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to sales</a></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-values\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-megaphone\"></i></div><h4>Pinned above free listings</h4><p>Premium partners appear before every other card within the city directory.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-envelope-paper\"></i></div><h4>Lead-friendly CTAs</h4><p>Direct website + phone buttons encourage bookings straight from this page.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h4>Always-on exposure</h4><p>Featured cards show even when we haven’t processed new static data yet.</p></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-grid\"><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"city-insights\" class=\"city-insights-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><section id=\"city-statistics\" class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db city-stats-unified\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-section-header\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-eyebrow\">City Statistics</span><h2 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">How <!-- -->Philadelphia<!-- --> stacks up for dog families</h2><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-intro\">Verified ratings, review volume, and park availability updated directly from our community directory.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stats-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card accent\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Community rating</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">4.6</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Average rating across every verified listing in Philadelphia. Reflects cleanliness, amenities, and community feedback.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Verified reviews</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">4,920</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Community reviews informing our quality score. Tap any park card below to see highlights.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Park availability</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">18</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Total verified listings currently live for Philadelphia. Fresh listings added weekly.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Indoor options</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">—</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Indoor options are being scouted—submit a favorite and we will feature it.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db data-grid-container\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db key-metrics-grid\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item primary\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-geo-alt-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">18</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Total Dog Parks</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-sub\">All types combined</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-star-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">4.6</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Average Rating</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-sub\">Based on <!-- -->4,920<!-- --> reviews</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-chat-heart-fill\"></i></div><div 