facility stands out for being professional and reliable and safe environment and great for socialization. Pet owners appreciate the attention to detail and the genuine care shown to every furry visitor. For more information, call (215) 482-8700. Visit their website for additional details.\",\"slug\":\"world-wide-aquarium-pets\",\"address\":\"7043 Ridge Ave\",\"street\":\"7043 Ridge Ave\",\"city\":\"Philadelphia\",\"state\":\"PA\",\"zipCode\":\"19128\",\"full_address\":\"7043 Ridge Ave, Philadelphia, PA 19128, USA\",\"latitude\":40.0446529,\"longitude\":-75.22989009999999,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJh4TOxN64xokRfdum4M9fFBg\",\"phone\":\"(215) 482-8700\",\"website\":\"https://worldwideridge.wixsite.com/worldwideaquarium/about-us\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.4,\"reviewCount\":685,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"10:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"10:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"10:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"10:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"10:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"10:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"10:00 AM – 6:00 PM\"},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJp68Ty61TwYkRwUur3tVsTO4\",\"name\":\"WOW Pets\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in Trevose rave about WOW Pets, giving it a solid 4.7-star rating based on 195 reviews. What makes this facility special is its clean and well-maintained, convenient location. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners is evident in every visit. For more information, call (267) 684-6625. Visit their website for additional details.\",\"slug\":\"wow-pets\",\"address\":\"1615 Loretta Ave\",\"street\":\"1615 Loretta Ave\",\"city\":\"Philadelphia\",\"state\":\"PA\",\"zipCode\":\"19053\",\"full_address\":\"1615 Loretta Ave, Trevose, PA 190