 makes this facility special is its clean and well-maintained, convenient location. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners is evident in every visit. For more information, call (267) 549-0077. Visit their website for additional details.\",\"slug\":\"ham-bone-queen-village\",\"address\":\"715 E Passyunk Ave\",\"street\":\"715 E Passyunk Ave\",\"city\":\"Philadelphia\",\"state\":\"PA\",\"zipCode\":\"19147\",\"full_address\":\"715 E Passyunk Ave, Philadelphia, PA 19147, USA\",\"latitude\":39.9399242,\"longitude\":-75.1513392,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJnweiULTJxokRBdjf0Y7YJbg\",\"phone\":\"(267) 549-0077\",\"website\":\"http://www.hamnbone.com/\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.8,\"reviewCount\":32,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"10:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"10:00 AM – 6:00 PM\"},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJEwPa5t_FxokRAlGoKAQy9n0\",\"name\":\"Jay's Exotic Reptiles & Plants\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Jay's Exotic Reptiles & Plants is a premier pet facility in Philadelphia that consistently earns praise from pet owners. With a 4.7-star rating from 87 reviews, This facility stands out for being professional and reliable and safe environment and great for socialization. Pet owners appreciate the attention to detail and the genuine care shown to every furry visitor. For more information, call (267) 702-5294. Visit their website for additional details.\",\"slug\":\"jay-s-exotic-reptiles-plants\",\"address\":\"1627 W Ritner St\",\"street\":\"1627 W Ritner St\",\"city\":\"Philadelphia\",\"state\":\"PA\",\"zipCode\